text: Winterhawk is a 1975 American western movie directed by Charles B. Pierce and starring Leif Erickson, Woody Strode, Denver Pyle, L. Q. Jones, Elisha Cook Jr., Seamon Glass, Ace Powell, Dawn Wells. It was distributed by Howco International Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1975 movies Category:1970s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Charles B.
